window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Everyone they love is in the past.</p> <p>The throne is in the future, it demands to be reckoned with.</p> <p>And Kaitlyn and Magnus must protect the son, no matter the cost. Even if it means losing it all.</p> <p>A blend of contemporary, historical, fantasy, and SciFi, <i>Son and Throne</i> is the eleventh book in the Kaitlyn and the Highlander series.</p> <p>If you love mysterious, sexy, hunky heroes with desperate hearts and romantic thoughts, heroines with courage who are also very ordinary disasters, and love stories that encompass all time, then you’ll love this romantic series. Listen on as Kaitlyn and Magnus protect their family by buying a copy of this audiobook today.</p> <ol> <li><i>Kaitlyn and the Highlander</i></li> <li><i>Time and Space Between Us</i></li> <li><i>A Warrior of My Own</i></li> <li><i>Begin Where We Are</i></li> <li><i>Entangled With You</i></li> <li><i>Magnus and a Love Beyond Words</i></li> <li><i>Under the Same Sky</i></li> <li><i>Nothing but Dust</i></li> <li><i>Again my Love</i></li> <li><i>Our Shared Horizon</i></li> </ol>"; 
